has_finite_products_of_has_products:

/-- If a category has all products then in particular it has finite products.
-/
theorem has_finite_products_of_has_products [has_products.{w} C] : has_finite_products C :=
  ⟨fun n => has_limits_of_shape_of_equivalence (discrete.equivalence equiv.ulift.{w})⟩
#align has_finite_products_of_has_products has_finite_products_of_has_products
has_finite_coproducts_of_has_coproducts:
/-- If a category has all coproducts then in particular it has finite coproducts.
-/
theorem has_finite_coproducts_of_has_coproducts [has_coproducts.{w} C] : has_finite_coproducts C :=
  ⟨fun J => has_colimits_of_shape_of_equivalence (discrete.equivalence equiv.ulift.{w})⟩
#align has_finite_coproducts_of_has_coproducts has_finite_coproducts_of_has_coproducts
